  "description": {
    "zh": "哇哦！慢着点，牛仔，我还有活儿给你干。你看...这个Ref混蛋以为能耍我们，你知道这家伙干了什么吗？他在死信盒里放了一包变质的牛奶，这tm是什么恶心的玩笑？总之，我猜我和他没有共同的幽默感，真是个怪胎...\n\n不过我还是查到了更多，显然他想把这批货弄出塔科夫，你知道我绝不能允许，那是我的财产！我的！他计划通过KPP营地用船把货运出这个地区，所以我需要派人混进去，别担心我不会派你进去，毕竟太危险了...\n\n所以我需要一套完整的Ratnik装备，一些标识和一个Terragroup钥匙卡，确保所有装备完好无损，并且直接交给我，别弄丢了，也绝对不要给其他任何索要这些东西的人，明白吗？如果你想耍什么小聪明，我会发现的，所以做正确的事，伙计。",
    "en": "Woah! Slow down there cowboy, I still have a job for you. You see... This Ref asshole thinks he can trick us, do you know what this guy did? He stashed a pack of spoiled milk at the dead drop, is this some kind of sick joke? Anyway, I guess me and him don't share the same sense of humour, what a weirdo...\n\nI managed to find out more though, apparently he wants to get this cargo out of Tarkov, and you know I can't afford that, that is my property! Mine! He is planning to ship it out of the region via the KPP camp, so I need a way to send someone inside there, and don't worry I won't send you inside of there, it's dangerous after all...\n\nSo I need a full ratnik loadout, some insignias and a Terragroup keycard, make sure all the gear is intact and bring all of the pieces directly to me, don't lose it and definitely don't give it to anyone else who is asking for this stuff, you got that? If you choose to play some dumb move, I will notice so do what's right buddy."
  },
